  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n: n^2 is even if and only if n is even. The classic fact used in the standard proof that sqrt(2) is irrational.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Cited directly via Mathlib's Nat.even_pow', which states Even (m^n) <-> Even m whenever the exponent n is nonzero; instantiated at exponent 2 with the nonzero side condition discharged by norm_num.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem even_sq (n : ℕ) : Even (n ^ 2) ↔ Even n",
